{
  "text": "We applied the co-ordinate ascent mean field variational inference (CAVI) [CITATION_1] Ghahramani & Beal, 2001 ) which assigns independent factors to the latent variables. The blueprint for corresponding CAVI updates are below and full derivations are presented in Supplementary section C.",
